3cp\u003e我觉得不必对一个高中生这么多的猜想和臆想，这仅仅就是一个高中生对自己的证明的自信和些许的年少不甘心而已，他只是渴望自己的天赋和才华被认同，而不是想要沽名钓誉，赚取名利。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以请不要恶意揣度了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560778512,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5d010439c6942c719879855eef3c2c2b","url_token":"xiao-zhu-luan-shi-yao-rao","name":"笑丶乱世妖娆","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-733b59aeccb7a4a79fccec2cd1a9972d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-733b59aeccb7a4a79fccec2cd1a9972d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5d010439c6942c719879855eef3c2c2b","user_type":"people","headline":"山巅劲松映朝阳，小爷弱冠当自强","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560778512","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545887083,"updated_time":1545950030,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e  我不想和你讨论学校的问题，我只想送给你一段话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  如果成功了，请千万不要骄傲，我希望若干年后对你的评价是：xxx，2019.1.1日证明了哥猜，从此一鸣惊人，成为世界著名数学家，解决了无数数学难题而不是xxx，曾经解决过哥猜，然后……没了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  如果失败了，也请千万不要气馁，毕竟你面对的是数学王冠上的明珠！无数知名数学家穷其一生都没能成功，而你年方18，风华正茂，以后还有机会。我只希望你此后更潜心于数学，最终走向数学之巅，成为你梦中的自己！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  最后，祝凯旋。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563109791,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ff34e812a24efb057ceb4e47222ccbe9","url_token":"zhang-lei-ting-69","name":"拉克秀","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3f5439fc7bab3aa6627850d4318f6877_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3f5439fc7bab3aa6627850d4318f6877_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ff34e812a24efb057ceb4e47222ccbe9","user_type":"people","headline":"低素质杠精一头","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563109791","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546182402,"updated_time":1546183224,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我能打赢比鲁斯，请问我有十五的战斗力吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我能下赢阿法狗，请问我有业余五段的实力吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我能默写辞海，请问我的文化水平有李逵高吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e能证明哥猜，这说明你在全球数学届，都是数的上号的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e谦虚点说，老子天下第一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e狂妄点说，我不是针对某一个人，我的意思是，地球上的各位，都是垃圾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最强高中生的称号是没得跑了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么牛逼的大爷，召来当学生？你说的是M78星云天顶星拖初七砍积极国的清北大学么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e反正不是地球上的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562783325,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562783325","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e88feffac997130323b05eb9d359c467_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546145719,"updated_time":1546145867,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e呦，真巧，我这几天也刚刚证出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 你说咱俩会不会就像牛顿和莱布尼兹一样，因为谁先创立了微积分的问题而争论不休呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e291370985c2226d650207f922239b51_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"104\" data-rawheight=\"80\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"104\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='104'%20height='80'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"104\" data-rawheight=\"80\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"104\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e291370985c2226d650207f922239b51_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e话说在前头，虽说你先声称自己证明出来了，但我的方法更胜一筹，绝对比你用的方法简洁。所以后人应该先提我的名字。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"340\" data-rawheight=\"287\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"340\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='340'%20height='287'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"340\" data-rawheight=\"287\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"340\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e好了，废话不多说，我的证明如下：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e首先，不妨先假设哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e那么，根据假设可知，哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e证明完毕。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简洁不简洁？思路是不是很清楚？你说我牛逼不牛逼？哈哈，我都佩服我自己。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e致后人：\u003c/b\u003e记得到时候提哥德巴赫猜想的时候，把我的名字放在“证明”老哥前面啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不说了，陪老婆去了。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e攒石党求求求求求求求欧气！！！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e愿我单抽出阿比！单抽出艾蕾！单抽出黑贞！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"727\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='727'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"727\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562750976,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"344aa4cb37f0857ab9d435bc0b5411ef","url_token":"ye-ji-dong-nan-xi-bei-fei","name":"野鸡东南西北飞","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1756b79837034fd0bb5ae9dac6bc315e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1756b79837034fd0bb5ae9dac6bc315e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/344aa4cb37f0857ab9d435bc0b5411ef","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562750976","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546141889,"updated_time":1546141889,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我高中的时候每次考试都能无视牛顿定律，篡改历史，创造语言，加速板块运动，改变人类基因，我骄傲了吗？没有！！！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562660757,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f476b16d98a7eda02c83663a0baa9db6","url_token":"wang-zhao-feng-60-19","name":"王兆丰","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/d76fff42d40f81af3887a2164ed17585_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/d76fff42d40f81af3887a2164ed17585_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f476b16d98a7eda02c83663a0baa9db6","user_type":"people","headline":"博士奶爸","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562660757","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546132084,"updated_time":1546132084,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"先回答问题～\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e能，当然能上清北！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e哥猜肯定不是个简单的问题。虽然我也不是很懂，但是从概率上来说，巅峰欧拉都无法证明，陈景润等人用了半生才半证明，我不相信你能证明。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e因为据我所知，在我们行业，这种级别的问题，你要自创一套体系才行。而且很大程度上你的这个体系不是突然提出的，前人或多或少都有提及和发展才能到解决哥猜的程度。而目前关于哥猜这个证明的研究进展，前面搞数学的大V已经回答或提到了，甚至贴出了相关论文，我看了一下其中的内容，个人觉得那绝对不是高中数学或高中自学能达到的水平。这个水平你肯定达不到，不是你智商或资质不够，而是需要时间才能消化吸收，你一出生就开始研究都不够。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e高考的压力的确很大，我当时也能感受到。如果你的问题是＂数学很好怎么保送清北？＂，相信知乎上很多人都会给你中肯的回答，甚至一些过来人能给你宝贵的建议。我的建议是修改问题，好好复习，争取一下，而不是说元旦发布证明过程这种上头的话。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e年轻的时候不能看轻自己，更不能过于看重自己。尤其是不自觉地消费自己，特别是在这个大网络时代。知乎上很多吃瓜群众都在消费你，这个问题成为一个大型审丑的事件。你一定不能陷进去，还是要脚踏实地点，即便你是个数学天才，因为天才特别容易陨落。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e如果说关于怎么保送清北的话，其实没必要这么麻烦，你只要发表1篇国内数学顶刊的文章，应该就有人会给你写清北自主招生的推荐信了，大概率会被清北录取，因为你已经一定程度证明了自己的学术能力。当然这只是我个人看法，请各位清北的大牛指正。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e再如果你只是想涨粉，那就好好运作吧，这世界实现自身价值的方法不止上清北一种，至少目前我看你很有炒作的天赋～\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e祝你顺利！","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561695219,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561695219","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545990072,"updated_time":1545990072,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e清华北大校长马上会动用私人关系限制你出境：这样的人才千万不能让哈佛抢了去。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561099774,"type":"answer","answer_type":"norm