ople","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560839754","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545892440,"updated_time":1545892440,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e孩子，刚学会走路甚至还不稳的时候不要想着能飞到外太空了吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许你真的对数学有那么一丢丢丢丢的“天分”，但是这点天分完全不足以让你去将哥猜证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只希望，你既然能这么心高气傲地有勇气肯定自己的证明，那么在1月1号你的论文发出来被各大神甚至只是普通研究数学的人指出错误的时候，你能有接受网络上所有对你的嘲笑和批判的勇气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后作为一个也学数学的普通人，我给你的建议是，先脚踏实地好好准备高考。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=820\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=780\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
